Module jakarta.xml.bind
Package jakarta.xml.bind

Interface Element

public interface Element
This is an element marker interface.

Under certain circumstances, it is necessary for the binding compiler to generate derived java content classes that implement this interface. In those cases, client applications must supply element instances rather than types of elements. For more detail, see section 5.7 "Element Declaration" and 5.7.1 "Bind to Java Element Interface" of the specification.
